                  <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-2">
                    <li><strong>Add child to Family&nbsp;Sharing.</strong> On the parent iPhone open <em>Settings › Family</em> › <em>Add Member</em> (or choose the child) and follow the prompts.</li>
                    <li><strong>Turn on Screen Time & set a passcode.</strong> Go to <em>Settings › Screen Time › [child]</em>, tap <em>Turn On Screen Time</em>, choose “This is My Child’s iPhone,” then create a 4-digit Screen Time passcode that’s different from the device unlock code.</li>
